DESCRIPTION:Looking for funding? Seeking a fellowship to support research?
  Want to fund travel for a summer project? Need dissertation support? Tak
 e this opportunity to learn how to search for funding by using a variety 
 of tools\, including the Duke Research Funding database\, MyResearchHome\
 , and Pivot. Open to Duke grad students\, postdocs\, faculty\, and staff.
   Zoom link will be provided after you register.\n\nThese workshops are r
 estricted to those with Duke affiliations. Registration is required.
